The second overall pick of the Heat in the 2008 NBA Draft will compete with forwards Rashard Lewis and James Jonesfor bench minutes if he makes the team. The Heat are taking a low-risk, high-reward flier on Beasley, bringing him into a veteran team that should allow the volatile talent an opportunity to carve out a role with less expectations than he had with Phoenix.
